  "Stefan Persson is Sweden's richest person by way of global cheap chic fashion retailer Hennes & Mauritz of which he owns 36%.",
  "Persson stepped down as chairman in May 2020 after 22 years in the role; his son Karl-Johan succeeded him.",
  "H&M was founded by Persson's father Erling in 1947.",
  "Persson's two other children, Charlotte Söderström and Tom Persson, and his sister Lottie Tham, are also billionaires."
